<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 02:23:27 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列人质在雷伊姆附近的聚会中被绑架，在囚禁期间被哈马斯谋杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostage-kidnapped-from-party-near-reim-murdered-by-hamas-while-in-captivity/0000018c-749a-d48b-a5ec-74dbea7f0000</link><description>27 岁的因巴尔·海曼 (Inbar Haiman) 成功躲避哈马斯恐怖分子两个小时，然后于 10 月 7 日被拖到加沙。她是一名涂鸦艺术家，正在学习视觉传达</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 01:55:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostage-kidnapped-from-party-near-reim-murdered-by-hamas-while-in-captivity/0000018c-749a-d48b-a5ec-74dbea7f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列南部贝都因小镇男子被枪杀，警方正在调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/man-shot-to-death-in-southern-israeli-bedouin-town-police-investigating/0000018c-7541-dbd5-a39c-ff7371ad0000</link><description>以色列警方怀疑这名 29 岁的男子因家庭不和而被枪杀。这起谋杀案是本周末发生的第三起疑似谋杀案</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 01:38:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/man-shot-to-death-in-southern-israeli-bedouin-town-police-investigating/0000018c-7541-dbd5-a39c-ff7371ad0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方逮捕两人并驱散以色列北部的反加沙战争抗议活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-arrest-two-disperse-anti-gaza-war-protest-in-northern-israel/0000018c-7496-d48b-a5ec-74d7d0d70000</link><description>参加示威的人数不到20人，但现场有很多警察。一名被拘留的抗议者说，我们站在那里进行合法的抗议守夜活动，没有打扰任何人。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 00:43:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-arrest-two-disperse-anti-gaza-war-protest-in-northern-israel/0000018c-7496-d48b-a5ec-74d7d0d70000</guid></item><item><title>获释人质在特拉维夫集会上发表讲话，要求释放协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/freed-hostages-address-tel-aviv-rally-to-demand-release-deal/0000018c-7467-dbd5-a39c-ff77679f0000</link><description>“我们警告说，战斗可能会伤害人质。不幸的是，我们是对的，”以色列军队在加沙战斗中误杀三名人质后，一名被释放的人质说道</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 22:37:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-17/ty-article/.premium/freed-hostages-address-tel-aviv-rally-to-demand-release-deal/0000018c-7467-dbd5-a39c-ff77679f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的两个战争目标发生致命冲突，加沙的每一天都让人质面临危险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/.premium/israels-two-war-aims-meet-for-a-fatal-clash-every-day-in-gaza-endangers-hostages/0000018c-73d3-d798-adac-f7ff8ca30000</link><description>地面入侵加沙已经六周了，很难想象遣返所有人质和摧毁哈马斯这两个目标能够同时实现。尽管家人提出要求，以色列并不急于恢复与哈马斯的谈判</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 19:53:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/.premium/israels-two-war-aims-meet-for-a-fatal-clash-every-day-in-gaza-endangers-hostages/0000018c-73d3-d798-adac-f7ff8ca30000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙被以色列国防军杀害的贝都因以色列人质的家人在葬礼后指责以色列和哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/.premium/after-funeral-of-bedouin-israeli-hostage-killed-by-idf-family-blames-israel-and-hamas/0000018c-7369-d798-adac-f7effe1e0000</link><description>被以色列国防军误杀的三名人质之一萨米尔·塔拉尔卡的葬礼于周六举行。他的父亲说，以色列军队必须“从所发生的事情中吸取教训”。萨默应该和我们在一起”</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 17:25:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/.premium/after-funeral-of-bedouin-israeli-hostage-killed-by-idf-family-blames-israel-and-hamas/0000018c-7369-d798-adac-f7effe1e0000</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，摩萨德负责人在欧洲会见卡塔尔总理，讨论以色列与哈马斯的人质交易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/.premium/mossad-chief-met-qatari-pm-in-europe-to-discuss-israel-hamas-hostage-deal-source-says/0000018c-7359-dbd5-a39c-ff7b9ac90000</link><description>以色列战时内阁将于周六召开会议，讨论继续接触的问题，但知情人士表示，以色列和哈马斯距离达成新协议还很遥远。据报道，摩萨德负责人还可能会见埃及高级官员</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 16:40:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/.premium/mossad-chief-met-qatari-pm-in-europe-to-discuss-israel-hamas-hostage-deal-source-says/0000018c-7359-dbd5-a39c-ff7b9ac90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军初步报告：被士兵杀害的人质挥舞着白旗，其中一人用希伯来语呼救</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/.premium/preliminary-idf-report-hostages-killed-by-soldiers-waved-white-flag-yelled-help-hebrew/0000018c-7283-db38-a9fc-fba363100000</link><description>报道称，悲剧发生两天前，以色列士兵在该地区发现了一栋建筑物，上面写着“SOS”和“救命！”在其中一堵墙上。以色列国防军部队在将该建筑物标记为可能的陷阱的区域行动</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 12:29:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/.premium/preliminary-idf-report-hostages-killed-by-soldiers-waved-white-flag-yelled-help-hebrew/0000018c-7283-db38-a9fc-fba363100000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗称已处决以色列摩萨德特工</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/iran-says-it-has-executed-an-israeli-mossad-spy/0000018c-7215-d798-adac-f6bfbe9f0000</link><description>伊朗官方媒体称，这名身份不明的男子与摩萨德等外国情报机构有联系，并被指控参与泄露机密信息</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 10:13:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/iran-says-it-has-executed-an-israeli-mossad-spy/0000018c-7215-d798-adac-f6bfbe9f0000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列人质被以色列国防军误杀后，数百人在特拉维夫集会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/.premium/hundreds-of-israelis-rally-in-tel-aviv-calling-for-immediate-release-of-hostages/0000018c-71c6-db38-a9fc-f9e608ee0000</link><description>以色列士兵在加沙地带将三名人质误认为是哈马斯成员，导致三名人质惨遭杀害，数百人走上特拉维夫街头，呼吁政府重返谈判桌，与哈马斯达成协议</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 09:33:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/.premium/hundreds-of-israelis-rally-in-tel-aviv-calling-for-immediate-release-of-hostages/0000018c-71c6-db38-a9fc-f9e608ee0000</guid></item><item><title>前人质：我们就加沙战斗向政府发出警告；世卫组织向希法医院运送物资</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article-live/hundreds-protest-in-tel-aviv-after-three-hamas-hostages-mistakenly-killed-by-idf/0000018c-707c-d798-adac-f4ff14b20000</link><description>以色列国防军在加沙误杀三名人质后，以色列人走上街头；以色列国防军负责人声称对死亡事件负责 ■ 加沙武装分子在地面行动中丧生 ■ 以色列国防军士兵在来自黎巴嫩的无人机袭击中丧生；以色列国防军袭击真主党目标 ■ 摩萨德负责人在欧洲会见卡塔尔总理，讨论新的人质协议 ■ 航运巨头因胡塞武装袭击而暂停红海交通 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵丧生；加沙至少 130 名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙 18,608 人死亡，50,594 人受伤</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 02:52:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article-live/hundreds-protest-in-tel-aviv-after-three-hamas-hostages-mistakenly-killed-by-idf/0000018c-707c-d798-adac-f4ff14b20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列可以从纽约 9/11 清理和纪念活动中学到什么</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/what-israel-can-learn-from-new-yorks-9-11-cleanup-and-commemoration/0000018c-6f95-db38-a9fc-efb71e8b0000</link><description>以色列不应该清除南部 10 月 7 日灾难的废墟，而应该学习纽约在 9 月 11 日之后所做的事情</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 23:20:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/what-israel-can-learn-from-new-yorks-9-11-cleanup-and-commemoration/0000018c-6f95-db38-a9fc-efb71e8b0000</guid></item><item><title>如果定居者的暴力还不够，以色列现在正在剥夺约旦河谷巴勒斯坦人的水源</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2023-12-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/if-settler-violence-wasnt-enough-israel-now-deprives-jordan-valley-palestinians-of-water/0000018c-6f70-dbd5-a39c-ff7344530000</link><description>自战争爆发以来，约 20 个巴勒斯坦家庭因定居者暴力加剧而被迫离开约旦河谷的家园。与此同时，军队不让牧羊人社区获得水源。以色列志愿者日夜努力保护他们</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 22:24:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2023-12-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/if-settler-violence-wasnt-enough-israel-now-deprives-jordan-valley-palestinians-of-water/0000018c-6f70-dbd5-a39c-ff7344530000</guid></item><item><title>随着“后天”辩论的临近，巴勒斯坦政治舞台对战后方向存在分歧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-arena-swings-between-poles-as-prospect-of-day-after-government-looms/0000018c-6cef-d798-adac-ecefe2e80000</link><description>哈马斯领导人最近的声明并不适合以色列人的耳朵，哈马斯不是也不必成为与以色列就解决加沙问题进行谈判的伙伴。伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚和穆萨·阿布·马尔祖克的言论针对巴勒斯坦人</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 22:10:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-arena-swings-between-poles-as-prospect-of-day-after-government-looms/0000018c-6cef-d798-adac-ecefe2e80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的“非殖民化”或巴勒斯坦人的“决定性失败”：这是我们唯一的选择吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/decolonization-of-israel-or-total-defeat-of-palestinians-are-these-our-only-options/0000018c-6f0f-d692-a9dc-7f9f1b040000</link><description>暴行铭刻在两国人民的历史记忆中。领导人实时谈论“以色列的毁灭”和“2023 年加沙浩劫”。在把我们全部吐出来之前，这个地球能吸收多少血？</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 21:43:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/decolonization-of-israel-or-total-defeat-of-palestinians-are-these-our-only-options/0000018c-6f0f-d692-a9dc-7f9f1b040000</guid></item><item><title>就连左派也喜欢以色列的“好阿拉伯人”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/even-the-leftists-are-loving-israels-good-arabs/0000018c-6eb5-dbd5-a39c-fff7d7d20000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 21:22:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/even-the-leftists-are-loving-israels-good-arabs/0000018c-6eb5-dbd5-a39c-fff7d7d20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列抗议者因加沙人质问题与联合国秘书长对峙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-protesters-confront-un-chief-over-hostages-held-in-gaza/0000018c-6ec2-d798-adac-eeeffd430000</link><description>人质被拖至加沙两个多月后，抗议者指责联合国秘书长安东尼奥·古特雷斯未能履行职责</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 20:28:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-protesters-confront-un-chief-over-hostages-held-in-gaza/0000018c-6ec2-d798-adac-eeeffd430000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队表示，他们在加沙北部杀害了三名人质，并被误认为是威胁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-killed-three-hostages-mistakenly-identified-as-threat-in-northern-gaza/0000018c-6edd-dbd5-a39c-ffff08470000</link><description>逃离囚禁并被以色列军队杀害的三名人质是 24 岁的 Samer Fuad El-Talalka、28 岁的 Yotam Haim 和 26 岁的 Alon Shamriz</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 20:15:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-killed-three-hostages-mistakenly-identified-as-threat-in-northern-gaza/0000018c-6edd-dbd5-a39c-ffff08470000</guid></item><item><title>“10 月 7 日发生的事情羞辱了以色列的男子气概。回应是暴力”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/what-happened-on-october-7-humiliated-israeli-masculinity-the-response-is-violence/0000018c-68bb-de43-affd-fcbb5fe40000</link><description>美国心理学家、女权主义学者卡罗尔·吉利根 (Carol Gilligan) 帮助改变了人们对女性道德观念的思考。她对男女关系的见解也与加沙战争有关</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 19:58:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/what-happened-on-october-7-humiliated-israeli-masculinity-the-response-is-violence/0000018c-68bb-de43-affd-fcbb5fe40000</guid></item><item><title>为什么很少有巴勒斯坦电影讲述加沙的故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/why-so-few-palestinian-films-tell-the-story-of-gaza/0000018c-6eb4-db38-a9fc-efb65b370000</link><description>20 世纪 90 年代烧毁电影院的狂热分子；前往西岸寻找机会的电影制片人；哈马斯政权完全蔑视西方文化——所有这些都阻止了巴勒斯坦电影在大银幕上描绘加沙的生活。只有几部电影能够讲述一些故事</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 19:06:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/why-so-few-palestinian-films-tell-the-story-of-gaza/0000018c-6eb4-db38-a9fc-efb65b370000</guid></item></channel></rss>